1. is_left_inverse_of [altcat_3]

Source [altcat_3]

definition
let C be non empty with_units AltCatStr ;
let o1, o2 be Object of C;
let A be Morphism of o1,o2;
let B be Morphism of o2,o1;
pred A is_left_inverse_of B means :: ALTCAT_3:def 1
A * B = idm o2;
end;
